WEBVTT

00:03.533 --> 00:05.633
Sig: THE OLDER I GET,
THE MORE AFRAID I AM

00:05.667 --> 00:09.500
OF BEING OUT
IN THE BERING SEA.

00:09.533 --> 00:11.100
THINGS DO HAPPEN.

00:11.133 --> 00:13.433
WATCH OUT, WATCH OUT, WATCH OUT!

00:13.467 --> 00:14.667
GET DOWN!

00:16.500 --> 00:19.000
OH, GOD.

00:19.033 --> 00:21.000
STORMS GO THROUGH,

00:21.033 --> 00:23.567
AND THEY CAN DESTROY
PEOPLE, BOATS,

00:23.600 --> 00:25.800
AND EVERYTHING IN ITS PATH.

00:25.833 --> 00:28.333
Man: WE'RE LAYING WAY
OVER ON OUR SIDE.

00:28.367 --> 00:30.300
FIVE PEOPLE ON THE BOAT.

00:30.333 --> 00:31.233
Man #2: MAN IN THE WATER.

00:31.267 --> 00:34.467
MAN OVERBOARD!
MAN OVERBOARD!

00:34.500 --> 00:36.733
Sig:
AND WE HAVE HAD OUR CLOSE CALLS.

00:36.767 --> 00:38.033
YOU SAVED
MY [BLEEP] LIFE, MAN.

00:38.067 --> 00:39.100
YOU SAVED
MY [BLEEP] LIFE.

00:39.133 --> 00:40.500
YOU SAVED
MY [BLEEP] LIFE.

00:40.533 --> 00:41.867
LEAVE THIS HERE.

00:41.900 --> 00:44.933
AND IT MAKES ME WONDER,
HOW MANY CHANCES DO WE GET?

00:46.867 --> 00:49.333
Woman: PAN-PAN.
PAN-PAN. PAN-PAN.

